headline: How Recent Analyst Shifts Are Shaping the Story for Cboe Global Markets
summary: Cboe Global Markets has recently seen its Fair Value estimate trimmed slightly, with the price target moving from $256.67 to $255.62. This adjustment comes amid mixed analyst sentiment, which includes bullish outlooks driven by strong core business revenues and bearish caution related to recent declines in the revenue capture rate for key options products.
